 137 HP!<br><br>/g wow, you all died?<br>xx tells the group, 'did a cleric camp?'<br>/g no clue<br>yy tells the group, 'crap, gonna be a long CR'<br>/g wow, solo exp is half a blue!<br>zz tells the group 'dude you F--ng lie!'<br>yy tells the group 'No Way!'<br>xx tells the group 'WOOOOOOOTTTT!!!!'<br><br>The only problem with this whole story?  My Wife tells me she's gonna kill me if I ever scream like that at 3 AM ever again ;)<br><br><br>So when's a time that you pulled magic right out of yer ass and saved your group/raid/soloing_self?  Or when's a time that you just really damn glad at that moment that you decided to play a Rogue over any other class?<br><br>--Demonspawn <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udroledefiantdagger.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Drole Defiantdagger</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/11/02 8:14:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22771.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Times when you love being a rogue</span><hr size=1> Getting a new max backstab on Fright right as he summoned me.<br><br>The bastard deserved all 323 points of damage too. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=2292><img src="http://brokenblades.phake.net/48thlvl2.gif" align="center"></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uihshanfalthenin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ihshan FalThenin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/11/02 9:18:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22771.topic&index=2